ANALYSIS
This bill extends the purpose of the education freedom savings account oversight committee to
include the review of student data, eligibility requirements, and EFA expenditures. The bill also
requires the committee to meet at a minimum monthly and for such meetings to be live broadcasted
aswellasrecordedonthegeneralcourtwebsite.
